	"system":{
		"description":{
			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>Two powerful hounds appear, growling thunder at your prey. They start circling it to cut off any escape.</i></p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Daily âœ¦ Acid, Summoning</b></p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Minor Action</b><b> &#8226; </b><b>Ranged</b> 5</p><p><b>Effect:</b> You summon two Medium hounds of the hunt, each appearing in an unoccupied square within range. Enemies grant combat advantage while adjacent to either hound. Each hound has a speed of 8 and a fly speed of 8 (hover). </p><p>Each hound has hit points equal to your healing surge value and uses your defenses, not including any temporary bonuses or penalties, with a +2 bonus to AC and Reflex. Each hound lasts until the end of the encounter or until it drops to 0 hit points. You lose a healing surge if both hounds are destroyed. </p><p>As a minor action, you can mentally direct both hounds to crawl, escape, run, stand up, shift, squeeze, or walk. The hounds do not need to perform the same action. </p><p>Published in Heroes of the Feywild, page(s) 124. </p>",
